data.description: This charming Home boasts a nicely painted exterior that adds a touch of vibrancy and character to its overall appeal. Step inside and you'll immediately appreciate the warm and inviting atmosphere, with natural light filling the space. The open concept layout seamlessly connects the living, dining and kitchen areas, creating an ideal space for entertaining. The spacious backyard offers ample room for outdoor activities, gardening, or simply relaxing in the fresh air. It provides a private retreat where one can unwind and enjoy the beauty of nature. So many updates done to the home throughout the years, such as, updated AC units, foundation repairs, updated plumbing, interior and exterior paint, expanded concrete patio space and much more. Schedule your showing today for a tour! Please note the grass has been digitally enhanced.
